######## Professor Falken's Puppet Modules ###########

A work in progress!

Details of each module can be found on http://www.threedrunkensysadsonthe.net 
and in the README file in each directory.

These modules _should_ just check out into your puppet module path

Please send all feedback to theprofessor@threedrunkensysadsonthe.net

